### 4.11 POST Transfer History - RESOURCE_MANAGEMENT (Expect 201 or 200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transfer-history
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transferId": 5,
  "previousStatus": "PENDING_DEPARTURE",
  "newStatus": "COMPLETED",
  "date": "2026-04-05T14:00:00Z",
  "userId": 3,
  "comment": "resource update"
}

###

